    },
    {
      "id": "elem_324_caf44819",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 850,
      "y": 6117,
      "width": 780,
      "height": 578,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "#f0faf0",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "elem_321_fb46d0f5"
      ],
      "roundness": {
        "type": 3,
        "value": 8
      },
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772141272276,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "elem_325_b134ee98",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 862,
      "y": 6128,
      "width": 558.42,
      "height": 548.0500000000001,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "elem_321_fb46d0f5"
      ],
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772141272276,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Triggered: user requests recommendations or opens Learn page\n\n 1. CURRICULUM_GET_RECOMMENDATIONS handler\n 2. Check CurriculumItem queue — return cached if queued items exist\n 3. gatherBubbleItems() -> fetch all learner items from DB\n 4. computeKnowledgeBubble(items) -> {\n      currentLevel (highest with >=80% coverage),\n      frontierLevel, levelBreakdowns (5 item types), gaps }\n 5. Compute: dueReviewCount + recentAccuracy (last 50 reviews)\n 6. generateCurriculumPlan({bubble, items, knownForms, dailyLimit, ...})\n    |-- computePacing() -> adjust daily target by debt/accuracy\n    |-- generateSpineAwarePlan():\n    |     Load curriculum-spine.json (cached)\n    |     Identify next uncompleted unit\n    |     getSpineBoosts() -> +0.5 supporting, +1.0 core items\n    |     generateRecommendations(with spineBoosts)\n    |-- filterByPrerequisites() -> remove gated grammar\n    |-- applyGrammarCap() -> max 2 grammar per day\n    |-- balanceVariety() -> interleave item types\n    |-- identifyReviewFocus() -> flag stuck items\n    |-- checkLevelProgression() -> levelUpReady?\n 7. If levelUpReady: seedNextLevelItems(userId, frontierLevel)\n    -> INSERT unseen items from frontier level in reference corpus\n 8. Persist plan.newItems to CurriculumItem table (status=queued)\n 9. Return CurriculumPlan to client\n\nUSER INTRODUCES ITEM:\n10. CURRICULUM_INTRODUCE_ITEM -> create LexicalItem/GrammarItem/ChunkItem\n    with mastery=introduced, mark CurriculumItem status=introduced\n\nItem types: lexical | grammar | collocation | chunk | pragmatic_formula",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Triggered: user requests recommendations or opens Learn page\n\n 1. CURRICULUM_GET_RECOMMENDATIONS handler\n 2. Check CurriculumItem queue — return cached if queued items exist\n 3. gatherBubbleItems() -> fetch all learner items from DB\n 4. computeKnowledgeBubble(items) -> {\n      currentLevel (highest with >=80% coverage),\n      frontierLevel, levelBreakdowns (5 item types), gaps }\n 5. Compute: dueReviewCount + recentAccuracy (last 50 reviews)\n 6. generateCurriculumPlan({bubble, items, knownForms, dailyLimit, ...})\n    |-- computePacing() -> adjust daily target by debt/accuracy\n    |-- generateSpineAwarePlan():\n    |     Load curriculum-spine.json (cached)\n    |     Identify next uncompleted unit\n    |     getSpineBoosts() -> +0.5 supporting, +1.0 core items\n    |     generateRecommendations(with spineBoosts)\n    |-- filterByPrerequisites() -> remove gated grammar\n    |-- applyGrammarCap() -> max 2 grammar per day\n    |-- balanceVariety() -> interleave item types\n    |-- identifyReviewFocus() -> flag stuck items\n    |-- checkLevelProgression() -> levelUpReady?\n 7. If levelUpReady: seedNextLevelItems(userId, frontierLevel)\n    -> INSERT unseen items from frontier level in reference corpus\n 8. Persist plan.newItems to CurriculumItem table (status=queued)\n 9. Return CurriculumPlan to client\n\nUSER INTRODUCES ITEM:\n10. CURRICULUM_INTRODUCE_ITEM -> create LexicalItem/GrammarItem/ChunkItem\n    with mastery=introduced, mark CurriculumItem status=introduced\n\nItem types: lexical | grammar | collocation | chunk | pragmatic_formula",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
